1. update CHANGELOG
2. bump version number in setup.py
3. check out a clean copy of the repository
   svn co http://pybluez.googlecode.com/svn/trunk pybluez
3. run python setup.py sdist
4. test installer
5. upload tarball to google code.
6. make sure outstanding changes are committed to SVN
7. create a tag
   svn copy https://pybluez.googlecode.com/svn/trunk https://pybluez.googlecode.com/svn/tags/pybluez_x_y_z
8. update webpage
